casebody.data:
The MONEY SOURCE, INC.
v.
Ryan KILBRIDE et al. Supreme Court of Connecticut. Decided May 22, 2019 Bobbi Ann Kilbride, self-represented, in support of the petition. Jeffrey M. Knickerbocker, in opposition.

The defendant Bobbi Ann Kilbride's petition for certification to appeal from the Appellate Court (AC 42339) is denied.
